it.unimi.di.law.bubing.frontier

Class WorkbenchEntrySet

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unimi.di.law.bubing.frontier.WorkbenchEntrySet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Hash, Serializable

    public class WorkbenchEntrySet
extends Object
implements Serializable, Hash
    A data structure representing the set of workbench entries created so far. It is a lightweight implementation of a map from IP addresses to workbench entries.
    See Also:
